library(magick)
#create picture1
meme1 <- image_read("https://img.36krcdn.com/20220128/v2_b75552449b724cc584cfd7ca6c476221_img_000?x-oss-process=image/format,jpg/interlace,1")%>%
  image_scale(400)
meme1

#create picture2
meme2 <- image_read("https://img.36krcdn.com/20220128/v2_0d2f182c015f4beea49026c58cedec63_img_000?x-oss-process=image/format,jpg/interlace,1")%>%
  image_scale(400)
meme2

#create picture3
meme3 <- image_blank(width = 400, 
                     height = 400, 
                     color = "#E2826E") %>%
  image_annotate(text = "cute emojy",
                 color = "#5FE68A",
                 size = 40,
                 font = "impact",
                 gravity = "center")
meme3

#create picture4
meme4 <-image_blank(width = 400, 
                    height = 400, 
                    color = "#50BBDB") %>%
  image_annotate(text = "cute cat",
                 color = "#D998F2",
                 size = 40,
                 font = "Impact",
                 gravity = "center")
meme4

#create my gif
meme5 <- c(meme1,meme3,meme2,meme4)
Final_image <- image_append(meme5)
image_write(Final_image, "my_animation.gi")
Final_image

#Creating a animation
meme_gif <- image_animate(meme5, fps = 1)
image_write(meme_gif,"my_animation.gif")
meme_gif
